item.title: CVE-2022-43414|2024-08-03T13:32:58.303Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20nunit%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins NUnit Plugin 0.27 and earlier implements an agent-to-controller message that parses files inside a user-specified directory as test results, allowing attackers able to control agent processes to obtain test results from files in an attacker-specified directory on the Jenkins controller.
